AttributesDescription: Equip to gain attributes, active skills, and specific effect bonuses.

Skill.DescriptionEx:
Basic Attack
Deal Fusion DMG equal to 200.00% of the active Resonator's ATK.

Core Skill
Brant Cube summons an anchor to attack, dealing Fusion DMG equal to 2720.00% of the active Resonator's ATK and generating a few Zesty Oranges when landed. Resonators who pick up the Zesty Oranges will have their ATK increased by 20% and their HP restored by 25% of the caster's Max HP for 12s, stacking up to 3 times. Skill Cooldown: 14s.

Enhanced Effect
Skill Projectiles Level 4/8: The number of Zesty Orange is increased by 2/4.
